    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Latex template use double braces instead of curly braces to mark jinja blocks, compare with the [shipped templates](https://github.com/jupyter/nbconvert/blob/master/nbconvert/templates/latex/report.tplx). Hence your template has to be adapted.\nMoreover, the latex templates are fundamentally different than the other, e.g. reveal templates. So you will have to base your pdf template on a latex template.\n"
